description:
Stuck on what to play or what to buy? Join TVGS as they list and discuss ten of the most over looked and obscure PSP hidden gems that are stuck on the Playstation Portable. Many lesser known games released for the PSP handheld console so let us know your top 10 overlooked games stuck on the console down below!
